👗La Sra. Harris va a París 
Año: 2022
Director: Anthony Fabian
País: Reino Unido
Donde Verla: HBO max
 
Holis! Hoy está peli que quería ver hace mucho y la he encontrado en una plataforma.

La historia me ha dejado un sabor dulce en la boca, dulce al igual que su protagonista la sra. Harris una mujer muy amable y cálida que pese a no ganar mucho dinero, sueña con ir a París y comprarse un vestido Dior.

Una señora que nos recuerda que en la vida si se pueden hacer realidad los sueños, sin importar que las demás personas te miren raro o les parezcan ridículos. 

Una peli conmovedora, llena de positivismo, fue un agrado ver a esta señora haciendo amigos tan fácilmente. 
Realmente me ha gustado muchísimo, no he parado de sonreír viéndola.

想說日本夏天的「お盆休み」（其實就是中國人的盂蘭節）

最初學日文時懶懶的只認漢字記意思
然後腦內一直都認錯做「お皿休み」(おさらやすみ)

到很後期才知道
是お盆(おぼん)，不是お皿(おさら)

*盆 =ぼんbon / 中文也是碗盆的盆意思
*皿 =さら sara / 中文是碗碟的碟的意思

然後一到夏天我說要穿浴衣去夏祭時
西給就會話：お皿(おさら)祭り😏？

😮‍💨好吧你笑吧

In our latest issue, we catalogue this season’s defining looks, which draw on ordinary materials presented in extraordinary compositions – an approach that resonates with the writings of Georges Perec, who explored the minute magnificence of everyday life.

Fashion fetishises the new, the outré, the extraordinary, but it’s our own thinking that keeps things feeling fresh. The whims for A/W23, namely the longer length of a jumper or the bumpier texture of leather, are just that. Here, someone in miumiu’s tobacco knit cardigan, matching knit top and chevron wool skirt uses their soft leather handbag as a pillow. Also pictured is an ‘Aluminium EA 117’ chair by Charles and Ray Eames for vitra. 

For more on this story, see the link in bio or Wallpaper’s September issue, on newsstands now.

Ganni SS24 ganni cphfw 

Ganni woman has become more sophisticated this collection. Tailoring brought elegance to the runway, some looks with fluidity whereas others had very strict silhouettes with a peplum flare. Leather and animal prints were responsible for the fun elements as well as embellishments, typical of Ganni. 

For this collection, the focus was not entirely on the garments, the styling had a key role in the show. Skirts over other skirts, elongated necklines that can stretch till almost your elbows or layering dresses caught many’s attention. 

The show was also the set to present their latest collaboration with newbalance , two pair of sneakers with Ganni’s logo in jewels.
